</a><sup>(62K, doc)</sup></span></p></div></div><div id="idm140065331843856" class="tsec sec"><h2 class="head no_bottom_margin" id="idm140065331843856title">Footnotes</h2><!--back/fn-group--><div class="fm-sec half_rhythm small"><p class="fn sec" id="idm140065331843728"><p id="__p114" class="p p-first"><strong>Authors\' contributions</strong></p><p id="__p115" class="p p-last">YJT and CHC conceived the study, developed the methodology, and wrote the manuscript. YSL performed the data analysis. HMW implemented the HCT-R2E algorithm and the GAP environment. All authors read and approved the final manuscript.</p></p></div></div><div id="idm140065329775744aff-info" class="tsec sec"><h2 class="head no_bottom_margin" id="idm140065329775744aff-infotitle">Contributor Information</h2><p><span class="fm-affl">Yin-Jing Tien, </span><span class="fm-affl"><span class="email-label">Email: </span><a href="mailto:dev@null" data-email="wt.ude.acinis.tats@yrag" class="oemail">wt.ude.acinis.tats@yrag</a></span>.</p><p><span class="fm-affl">Yun-Shien Lee, </span><span class="fm-affl"><span class="email-label">Email: </span><a href="mailto:dev@null" data-email="wt.ude.ucm@kcajob" class="oemail">wt.ude.ucm@kcajob</a></span>.</p><p><span class="fm-affl">Han-Ming Wu, </span><span class="fm-affl"><span class="email-label">Email: </span><a href="mailto:dev@null" data-email="wt.ude.ukt.liam@uwmh" class="oemail">wt.ude.ukt.liam@uwmh</a></span>.</p><p><span class="fm-affl">Chun-Houh Chen, </span><span class="fm-affl"><span class="email-label">Email: </span><a href="mailto:dev@null" data-email="wt.ude.acinis.tats@nehcc" class="oemail">wt.ude.acinis.tats@nehcc</a></span>.</p></div><div id="Bib1" class="tsec sec"><h2 class="head no_bottom_margin" id="Bib1title">References</h2><div class="ref-list-sec sec" id="reference-list"><div class="ref-cit-blk half_rhythm" id="CR1">1. <span class="element-citation">Eisen MB, Spellman PT, Brown PO, Botstein D. Cluster analysis and display of genome-wide expres